WEBVTT

00:06:29.447 --> 00:06:31.316
It requires a racial literacy.

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:34.704
Now, how do parents
have these conversations,

00:06:34.728 --> 00:06:36.699
and what is a racial literacy?

00:06:36.723 --> 00:06:37.912
Thank you for asking.

00:06:37.936 --> 00:06:39.161
(Laughter)

00:06:39.185 --> 00:06:43.520
A racial literacy involves
the ability to read,

00:06:43.544 --> 00:06:46.595
recast and resolve
a racially stressful encounter.

00:06:47.348 --> 00:06:50.766
Reading involves recognizing
when a racial moment happens

00:06:50.790 --> 00:06:52.858
and noticing our stress reactions to it.

00:06:53.958 --> 00:06:55.584
Recasting involves

00:06:56.830 --> 00:07:01.775
taking mindfulness and reducing
my tsunami interpretation of this moment